subject: Football (College)
organizations: North Carolina Agricultural and Technical State University
lead_paragraph: Tarik Cohen rushed for 295 yards and three touchdowns of 73 or more yards, and North Carolina A&T used a slew of big plays for a 41-34 win over Alcorn State.
